{"tid":504974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8華人加入贊比亞輔警　激怒民眾不足一日被炒","createTime":"2017-12-20T15:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T12:28:32.000Z","uid":5195,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e3b0085774f37281e60f90c2cbdc97c2589361ea","tid":504974,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T15:39:58.000Z","msg":"中非國家贊比亞的輔警部隊最近招募了8名華人隊員，並於周一（18日）在首都盧薩卡的贊比亞華僑華人總會舉行入隊儀式。贊比亞警察總監坎甘加、中國駐贊比亞大使館領事部主任趙民及僑社代表均有出席儀式。惟警方的態度於不足一日後出現180度轉變，以激怒當地民眾為由，撤去8人的職務。<br />\n<br />\n親自為8名新成員頒發證件的坎甘加形容，警方自身力量有限，在打擊犯罪活動時有不少限制，必需要社會各界支持，聯手撲滅罪行；趙民則指華人成為輔警顯示出贊比亞警方及中國僑社互相信任，期望大家能互相合作有效地維持治安。<br />\n<br />\n有英國傳媒報道，坎甘加事後火速撤去輔警的職務。前總統發言人支持坎甘加的決定，又指坎甘加的做好符合憲法的規定。贊比亞警方發言人表示，接到民眾的投訴後，經過協商後決定撤去華人輔警，惟他強調招攬華人輔警不違反憲法規定。贊比亞年初通過新法律，禁止任何與外國公民通婚的贊比亞人及雙重國籍人士加入警隊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171220/photo/bknint-20171220060026550-1220_17011_001_01p.jpg?20171220150743\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171220%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20171220060026550-1220_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20171220150743&h=fdef5952&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c180b1b476eadc8f16324d96252d262c2007c06","tid":504974,"uid":62599,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T15:44:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec288c141a75553dc6851f6b4f15edffacd9782f","tid":504974,"uid":56624,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:21:56.000Z","msg":"支那人入慘世界各國警隊，齊齊共享公安榮譽"},{"pid":"2b86741a85fd1443eda97f558fa1ea3e3708b1d2","tid":504974,"uid":8478,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:30:40.000Z","msg":"非洲人都頂唔順支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41588d22f5d1bb35ac450163c52c46825cc74e5f","tid":504974,"uid":9542,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T23:24:16.000Z","msg":"以前廿一條<br />\n中國警察由中日合辦或聘用日本顧問<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9edbee675dd9dd3b1b35d3dcf83a880b4b3fe5b3","tid":504974,"uid":56999,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T23:43:15.000Z","msg":"大陸人：給錢，不然抓你回去行政拘留<br />\n非洲人：不可貪污行賄<br />\n中陸人：什麼？!操你媽個b 非洲不準收錢的嗎"},{"pid":"18a3f7892e2fa3052a49f68703de9af914499507","tid":504974,"uid":163144,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:52:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"050b405dc53518651013f73bb779a5962b37d54b","tid":504974,"uid":18587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:08:11.000Z","msg":"肯撚死走去收鳩人錢啦！"},{"pid":"4036f9d28d352bc0aa6b0819a0e3b39473fc0c96","tid":504974,"uid":67346,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:12:46.000Z","msg":"屌上面死返去電訊台啦"},{"pid":"bbe13fbf2b57342cceff3c308788588ef13c3a61","tid":504974,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b41b0c25670170e20c3be274b159a27b415e9da","tid":504974,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b662f9ea1ac19828105446d758a674cc31f6ad5f","tid":504974,"uid":83569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:28:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>非洲人都頂唔順支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji